    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document deprecates the use of the RSASHA1 and
RSASHA1-NSEC3-SHA1 algorithms for the creation of DNS Public Key
(DNSKEY) and Resource Record Signature (RRSIG) records.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It updates RFCs 4034 and 5155 as it deprecates the use of these
algorithms.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
